Claire Trevor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claire_Trevor 0 Claire Trevor (born Claire Wemlinger; March 8, 1910 – April 8, 2000) was an American actress. She appeared in over 60 films, winning the Academy Award for Best Supporting Actress for her role in Key Largo, and earning nominations for her roles in The High and the Mighty and Dead End. She also received top billing in Stagecoach. Claire_Trevor ( born Claire_Wemlinger ; March_8_,_1910 – April_8_,_2000 ) was an_American_actress .
